      484.12,
      531.41,
      524.95
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces and in Galle, Matara, Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts after 1.00 p.m.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
