  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.32,
      567.46,
      533.87,
      603.67
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa and Uva provinces and in Ampara and Polonnaruwa districts during the early hours of the morning.",
